metadata.name: Bus Ride
metadata.description: As our buses passed one another, I caught a glimpse of her, she was oblivious to her surroundings, deep in thought, I was only able to snap one photo as we passed and she has been on my mind ever since. What could have been on her mind? I see her and I reflect on my own life, am I making the best of it? What have I accomplished? Have I loved enough?
